HEADWORD: Canorous
<hw>Ca*no"rous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>canorus</ets>, from <ets>nor</ets> melody, fr. <ets>canere</ets> to
sing.]</ety> <def>Melodious; musical.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Birds that are most
